title: About
text:
Hello, I’m Wookyoung Ahn, welcome to my site! I’m a junior student in the English Language and Literature Department at KSNU. I love English!
I took a computer English class for one semester and studied a lot of things, including RStudio.

title: My favorite things
text:
Let me introduce you to some of my favorite things.

I love ice cream, especially vanilla ice cream.

One of my favorite is cute animal! I like hamster, puppy, kitten, lizard.

I have 5 lizards. This lizard looks like my Dorong, Crested gecko.

title: my future
text:
My dream job is to become a public sector clerk. I want to work at the National Health Service and be responsible for health policies.

My bucket list includes a solo trip to Dubai and a desert tour. I want to experience the mystique of the desert and Dubai’s skyscrapers together.
